By Staff
On the day before her 8-year-old, Jayanna Powell, was killed by a hit-and-run driver in West Philadelphia, Ayeshia Poole shot a cellphone video of her daughter.
“‘Mommy, I love you,’” the girl had said on the video, a weeping Poole told a judge on Friday. “I listen to that tape every day.”
